lead_paragraph: Belgium winger Adnan Januzaj sustained what looked like a hamstring injury while playing for Manchester United under-21s against Norwich City on Monday, the club's website has reported.

headline.print_headline: Winger Januzaj Limps Out of Manchester United Reserves Match
